  "detailed_description": "Survivor Alliance is a survivor like game that combines zombie and pigeon elements, where players take on the role of a human survivor fighting against zombies in a world dominated by zombies. Upgrade by killing zombies and selecting appropriate skills and items to survive.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150150/extras/a6e392f5c5b70c5492ebe0c4ca67b4ed.poster.avif?t=1727847050\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150150/extras/a6e392f5c5b70c5492ebe0c4ca67b4ed.webm?t=1727847050\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150150/extras/a6e392f5c5b70c5492ebe0c4ca67b4ed.mp4?t=1727847050\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The virus has spread globally, but humanity is far from giving up. Face your fear, transform into a warrior guarding humanity, and repel the zombies.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150150/extras/d74a11582733e43026afd88a35e1f1ee.poster.avif?t=1727847050\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150150/extras/d74a11582733e43026afd88a35e1f1ee.webm?t=1727847050\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150150/extras/d74a11582733e43026afd88a35e1f1ee.mp4?t=1727847050\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Upgrade battles, strengthen your weapons, change their form, and defeat zombies with more powerful weapons.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150150/extras/594a6fa505adb5da5e038dff4dda3a2d.poster.avif?t=1727847050\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150150/extras/594a6fa505adb5da5e038dff4dda3a2d.webm?t=1727847050\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150150/extras/594a6fa505adb5da5e038dff4dda3a2d.mp4?t=1727847050\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>During the game, you will encounter supplies from the base, with some powerful items randomly appearing inside. Some can enhance your firearms and weapons, while others can improve your survival ability. Choosing them wisely is the key to becoming stronger.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150150/extras/732ef61b3bb97f4b45eb4e8be754a99e.poster.avif?t=1727847050\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150150/extras/732ef61b3bb97f4b45eb4e8be754a99e.webm?t=1727847050\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150150/extras/732ef61b3bb97f4b45eb4e8be754a99e.mp4?t=1727847050\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>During the battle, if you encounter different survivors, you can invite them to join the team or send them back to the safe zone to receive rewards. Build teams with different styles according to your preferences.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150150/extras/f5da995783967dad13e491c2a266dce8.poster.avif?t=1727847050\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150150/extras/f5da995783967dad13e491c2a266dce8.webm?t=1727847050\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150150/extras/f5da995783967dad13e491c2a266dce8.mp4?t=1727847050\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Build your favorite team through permanent upgrades. Determine your upgrade direction, pursue your favorite profession, and upgrade accordingly to become the guardian of the world.",
  "about_the_game": "Survivor Alliance is a survivor like game that combines zombie and pigeon elements, where players take on the role of a human survivor fighting against zombies in a world dominated by zombies. Upgrade by killing zombies and selecting appropriate skills and items to survive.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150150/extras/a6e392f5c5b70c5492ebe0c4ca67b4ed.poster.avif?t=1727847050\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150150/extras/a6e392f5c5b70c5492ebe0c4ca67b4ed.webm?t=1727847050\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150150/extras/a6e392f5c5b70c5492ebe0c4ca67b4ed.mp4?t=1727847050\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The virus has spread globally, but humanity is far from giving up. Face your fear, transform into a warrior guarding humanity, and repel the zombies.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150150/extras/d74a11582733e43026afd88a35e1f1ee.poster.avif?t=1727847050\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150150/extras/d74a11582733e43026afd88a35e1f1ee.webm?t=1727847050\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150150/extras/d74a11582733e43026afd88a35e1f1ee.mp4?t=1727847050\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Upgrade battles, strengthen your weapons, change their form, and defeat zombies with more powerful weapons.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150150/extras/594a6fa505adb5da5e038dff4dda3a2d.poster.avif?t=1727847050\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150150/extras/594a6fa505adb5da5e038dff4dda3a2d.webm?t=1727847050\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150150/extras/594a6fa505adb5da5e038dff4dda3a2d.mp4?t=1727847050\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>During the game, you will encounter supplies from the base, with some powerful items randomly appearing inside. Some can enhance your firearms and weapons, while others can improve your survival ability. Choosing them wisely is the key to becoming stronger.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150150/extras/732ef61b3bb97f4b45eb4e8be754a99e.poster.avif?t=1727847050\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150150/extras/732ef61b3bb97f4b45eb4e8be754a99e.webm?t=1727847050\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150150/extras/732ef61b3bb97f4b45eb4e8be754a99e.mp4?t=1727847050\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>During the battle, if you encounter different survivors, you can invite them to join the team or send them back to the safe zone to receive rewards. Build teams with different styles according to your preferences.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150150/extras/f5da995783967dad13e491c2a266dce8.poster.avif?t=1727847050\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150150/extras/f5da995783967dad13e491c2a266dce8.webm?t=1727847050\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150150/extras/f5da995783967dad13e491c2a266dce8.mp4?t=1727847050\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Build your favorite team through permanent upgrades. Determine your upgrade direction, pursue your favorite profession, and upgrade accordingly to become the guardian of the world.",
